  ('optometrist-moex-00101', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關單眼自覺式驗光流程，請排出下列最適合的順序：①傑克森交叉圓柱鏡（Jacksoncrossedcylinder,JCC）', '["最大正球面度最佳視力（maximumplustomaximumvisualacuity）的球面度數", "霧視至20/40 至20/60", "傑克森交叉圓柱鏡JCC軸度確認  ⑤紅綠檢查", "⑤"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "99730c6ed7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "273f9b848536", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00102', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於視力表與視力檢查，下列何者最不適當？', '["LogMAR視力值與史奈倫視力值（Snellenacuity）並不相同，所以比較不同類型視力表時要小心", "LogMAR視力表視標大小的遞增，是基於字母的關鍵視角取以10為底的對數之後的數值", "LogMAR視力表視標的關鍵視角是以角分（minutesofarc）為單位", "病人能看到的LogMAR視力表的最小字母，我們可以視為其最大解析角（maximumangleofresolution, MAR）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "99730c6ed7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "273f9b848536", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
